sun.jvm.hotspot.utilities

Class AddressOps

  • java.lang.Object
    • sun.jvm.hotspot.utilities.AddressOps

  • public class AddressOps
extends java.lang.Object
    Helper class with operations on addresses. Solves the problem of one or both of the arguments being null and needing to call methods like greaterThan(), lessThan(), etc. on them.
